title: Queen Latifah Queen By Queen Latifah For Women Eau De Parfum Spray, 3.4-Ounce / 100 Ml
description: Queen Eau De Parfum Spray 3.4 Oz / 100 Ml For Women By Queen Latifah. Sultry, Sensual, Remarkably Rare Baie Rose Harmonizes With Jasmine Noir, While Cognac, Authoritative And Intriguing, Meets Aromatic Moroccan Coriander As The Heart Of The Fragrance and Comes To Life. The Base Notes Create A Powerful, Mysterious Accord For This Deep, Rich Oriental Fragrance: Indonesian Patchouli And Precious Sandalwood Enhance The Soft Allure Of Vanilla And Tonka Absolute. The Fragrance Finishes With A Graceful Sojourn Made Memorable With Passionate Egyptian Incense And Sexy Musk.When applying any fragrance please consider that there are several factors which can affect the natural smell of your skin and, in turn, the way a scent smells on you.  For instance, your mood, stress level, age, body chemistry, diet, and current medications may all alter the scents you wear.  Similarly, factor such as dry or oily skin can even affect the amount of time a fragrance will last after being applied

title: Queen of Hearts Latifah Eau De Parfum Spray for Women, 1.7 Ounce
description: Launched by the design house of Queen Latifah in the year 2010.
